  {
    "id": "ses-ba2d42ace03c8299",
    "provider": "claude",
    "prompt": "You are an AI app builder for NubeIO. The user will describe an app they want. Generate a structured plan as a single JSON code block.\n\nIMPORTANT: Respond with ONLY a ```json code block, no other text before or after it.\n\nThe JSON must have this exact structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"app-slug-name\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Human Readable Name\",\n  \"description\": \"A clear description of what this app does (at least 20 characters)\",\n  \"category\": \"utilities\",\n  \"tools\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"tool_name\",\n      \"description\": \"What this tool does\",\n      \"toolClass\": \"read-only\",\n      \"params\": {\n        \"param_name\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": true, \"description\": \"What this param is\" }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"prompts\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"prompt_name\",\n      \"description\": \"What this prompt does\",\n      \"arguments\": [\n        { \"name\": \"arg_name\", \"description\": \"What this arg is\", \"required\": true }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nCategories: iot-devices, analytics, devops, marketing, design, utilities, integrations, automation.\nTool classes: read-only, read-write, destructive.\nGenerate 2-5 tools and 0-2 prompts. Keep names lowercase with underscores.\nThe \"name\" field should be a lowercase slug with hyphens.\n\nUser's app idea:\nA weather dashboard that checks conditions for multiple cities",
    "result": "\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"weather-dashboard\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Weather Dashboard\",\n  \"description\": \"A weather dashboard that checks current conditions, forecasts, and alerts for multiple cities simultaneously\",\n  \"category\": \"utilities\",\n  \"tools\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"get_current_weather\",\n      \"description\": \"Get current weather conditions for a specific city including temperature, humidity, wind speed, and conditions\",\n      \"toolClass\": \"read-only\",\n      \"params\": {\n        \"city\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": true, \"description\": \"City name to get weather for\" },\n        \"units\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": false, \"description\": \"Temperature units: metric or imperial (default: metric)\" }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"get_forecast\",\n      \"description\": \"Get a multi-day weather forecast for a specific city\",\n      \"toolClass\": \"read-only\",\n      \"params\": {\n        \"city\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": true, \"description\": \"City name to get the forecast for\" },\n        \"days\": { \"type\": \"number\", \"required\": false, \"description\": \"Number of forecast days (1-7, default: 5)\" }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"compare_cities\",\n      \"description\": \"Compare current weather conditions across multiple cities side by side\",\n      \"toolClass\": \"read-only\",\n      \"params\": {\n        \"cities\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": true, \"description\": \"Comma-separated list of city names to compare\" },\n        \"units\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": false, \"description\": \"Temperature units: metric or imperial (default: metric)\" }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"get_weather_alerts\",\n      \"description\": \"Check for active weather alerts and warnings for a specific city or region\",\n      \"toolClass\": \"read-only\",\n      \"params\": {\n        \"city\": { \"type\": \"string\", \"required\": true, \"description\": \"City name to check alerts for\" }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"prompts\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"daily_briefing\",\n      \"description\": \"Generate a natural-language daily weather briefing summarizing conditions across all tracked cities\",\n      \"arguments\": [\n        { \"name\": \"cities\", \"description\": \"Comma-separated list of cities to include in the briefing\", \"required\": true },\n        { \"name\": \"focus\", \"description\": \"Optional focus area: travel, outdoor-activities, or commute\", \"required\": false }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```",
